PidFile	/run/opendkim/opendkim.pid
Mode	v
Syslog	yes
SyslogSuccess	yes
LogWhy	yes
UserID	opendkim:opendkim
Socket	inet:8891@localhost
Umask	002
SendReports	yes
SoftwareHeader	yes
Canonicalization	relaxed/relaxed
Selector	default
MinimumKeyBits	1024
KeyFile	/etc/opendkim/keys/default.private
